lyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/division-sahabah-surah-juz\/","url_meta":{"origin":14036,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Quran: How companions divided the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aws ibn Hudhayfah reported: I asked the companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, how they divided the Quran. They said, \u201cThree chapters, then five, then seven, then nine, then eleven, then thirteen, and then al-Mufassal as a single part.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1393\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/prophet-recite-quran-nawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":14036,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: The Prophet recites Quran before sleep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would not sleep in his bed until he has recited Surat Bani Isra\u2019il and Al-Zumar. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2920 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0641\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u062d\u064e\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u064a\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3987,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/dajjal-ten-verses-kahf\/","url_meta":{"origin":14036,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: Verses of Al-Kahf protect from False Messiah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever memorizes ten verses from the beginning of Surat al-Kahf\u00a0will be immune to the False Messiah.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"From the last ten verses of Surat al-Kahf.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 809 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3984,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/sakina-surat-al-kahf\/","url_meta":{"origin":14036,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sakinah: Tranquility descends with Quran recitation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: A man was reciting Surat al-Kahf, and an animal became unsettled in his barn. As he looked, there was a mist or a cloud overshadowing him. The man mentioned that to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \"Keep reciting, O you,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/surat-al-kahf-friday-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":14036,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Kahf: Reading Surat al-Kahf on Friday brings light","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites Surat al-Kahf on Friday, a light will shine for him between this Friday and the next.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 5996 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3870,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/last-ayat-surah-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14036,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Last two verses of al-Baqarah sufficient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites the last two verses of Surat al-Baqarah in the night, it is enough for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 807 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14036","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14036"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14036\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14036"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14036"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14036"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}